title: Vray for x64/x32/x86 bit- 3ds max 2009 [no watermarks]
description:
I had to search far and wide for a x32 bit install. Been scanned by avast. 


Instructions are easy, install as normal. go look for the crack file and:


Put "vray2009.dll" to 3ds Max 2009 root directory
Put "vrender2009.dlr" to ...3ds Max 2009plugins
Put "VrayAASettingsFIX.ms" to ...3ds Max 2009ScriptsStartup

First upload here, let me know what else you need. 

EDIT: please help seed too.
